`@platejs/selection`

### Bug Fixes

- Added `disableSelectAll` option to **BlockSelectionPlugin**. Set to `true` to disable the plugin's custom selectAll (Cmd+A) behavior and use the editor's default behavior instead. ([#4799](https://github.com/udecode/plate/pull/4799))

        ```ts
        BlockSelectionPlugin.configure({
          options: { disableSelectAll: true },
        });
        ```

