`@platejs/combobox`

### Bug Fixes

- Add `getUserId` option to `TriggerComboboxPluginOptions` to fix combobox popover opening for all users in Yjs collaboration mode ([#4762](https://github.com/udecode/plate/pull/4762))

    When a user types a trigger character (e.g. `/` or `@`), the combobox input now stores the creator's `userId`. Only the creator will see the auto-focused combobox popover.

    ```tsx
    SlashPlugin.configure({
      options: {
        getUserId: (editor) => editor.getOption(YjsPlugin, "userId"),
      },
    });

    MentionPlugin.configure({
      options: {
        getUserId: (editor) => editor.getOption(YjsPlugin, "userId"),
      },
    });
    ```

